name: cmd_list_gen
description: - *Bot Owner Only* commands refer to the commands only the **owner** of the bot can use. - *Bot Owner Only* commands do **not** refer to the owner of the **server**, just the owner of the **bot**. - *Owner of the bot* is a person who is **hosting** their own bot, and their **ID** is inside of **credentials.json** file. - You are **not** the bot **owner** if you invited the bot using **Carbonitex** or other invitation links.
author: zfbx
